979
01:42:34,814 --> 01:42:38,489
[ Crowd Cheering ]

980
01:42:41,974 --> 01:42:44,283
[ Deacon ]
0ur guide in the wild.

981
01:42:44,374 --> 01:42:46,649
[ Deacon ]
0ur beacon in the darkness.

982
01:42:46,734 --> 01:42:48,565
