is upon us,

986
01:42:59,014 --> 01:43:02,324
let's sacrifice one
to old Saint Joe.

987
01:43:05,374 --> 01:43:08,844
And let's get this
tub of shit up to speed.

988
01:43:14,654 --> 01:43:16,565
Yep.

989
01:43:23,934 --> 01:43:26,732
[ Wild Cheering ]

990
01:43:53,014 --> 01:43:54,845
Pull!

991
01:43:54,934 --> 01:43:57,494
- Pull!
- Pull!

992
01:43:57,534 --> 01:43:59,604
- Pull.
- Pull!

993
01:44:13,534 --> 01:44:15,365
0w.

994
01:44:18,774 --> 01:44:21,925
