996
01:44:23,934 --> 01:44:26,767
They'll row for a month
before they figure out l'm fakin' it.

997
01:44:26,814 --> 01:44:29,374
But, um, wh-wh--

998
01:44:29,454 --> 01:44:32,446
0h, you want details.
