cut 'em out of her goddamn back.

1001
01:44:41,294 --> 01:44:44,525
Who is that?
Who is that?

1002
01:44:45,574 --> 01:44:47,929
Maybe one of
the spare rowers?

1003
01:44:55,534 --> 01:44:58,173
Why aren't you rowin'?

1004
01:45:06,374 --> 01:45:08,410
- lt's him.
- lt is him.

1005
01:45:09,734 --> 01:45:12,294
You guys are in
so much trouble.

1006
01:45:15,014 --> 01:45:19,212
Well, l'll be damned.
lt's the gentleman guppy.

1007
01:45:19,294 --> 01:45:22,923
You know, he's like
a turd that won't flush.

1008
01:45:22,974 --> 01:45:25,534
l want the girl.

1009
01:45:27,854 --> 01:45:32,803
You know, l thought you
were stupid, friend.

1010
01:45:32,894 --> 01:45:35,692
- [ Gun Cocking ]
- But l underestimated you.

1011
01:45:35,774 --> 01:45:38,652
You're a total freakin' retard.

1012
01:45:38,734 --> 01:45:41,692
[ Laughing ]

1013
01:45:41,734 --> 01:45:44,851
l want the girl. That's all.

1014
01:45:44,894 --> 01:45:49,524
