1025
01:46:31,134 --> 01:46:33,967
l mean, you're gonna
die for your friend.

1026
01:46:35,294 --> 01:46:37,171
lf it comes to that.

1027
01:46:39,374 --> 01:46:43,606
- He's bluffing. l'll kill him.
- He's not bluffing. He never bluffs.

1028
01:46:43,694 --> 01:46:44,843
Shut up!

1029
01:46:46,134 --> 01:46:51,083
l don't-- l-l-- l don't think
you're gonna drop that torch, my friend.

1030
01:46:51,134 --> 01:46:54,649
