1031
01:46:58,054 --> 01:47:00,727
No!

1032
01:47:07,414 --> 01:47:10,008
0h, thank God.

1033
01:47:13,654 --> 01:47:16,248
[ Screaming ]

1034
01:47:21,294 --> 01:47:24,286
[ Gunfire ]

1035
01:47:26,254 --> 01:47:28,449
[ Smoker ]
Look out! [ Screaming ]

1036
01:47:28,534 --> 01:47:30,923
Get him!

1037
01:47:30,974 --> 01:47:34,330
Let's go, goddamn it!

1038
01:47:34,414 --> 01:47:38,965
- [ Screaming ]
- Don't just stand there!
Kill somethin'!

1039
01:47:42,014 --> 01:47:43,845
Was this your big vision?

1040
01:47:47,654 --> 01:47:50,452
[ Screaming ]

1041
01:47:52,214 --> 01:47:55,968
0h, yeah! l've always wanted
to drive this monster.

1042
01:47:59,134 --> 01:48:02,171
There he is!
There he is!

1043
01:48:05,134 --> 01:48:07,409
That's him! There!

1044
01:48:09,534 --> 01:48:11,923
[ Shrieks ]

1045
01:48:14,214 --> 01:48:17,092
[ Screaming ]

1046
01:48:19,774 --> 01:48:23,244
