[ Laughing ]
You should've stayed underwater.

1054
01:48:51,934 --> 01:48:54,687
[ Clicks Twice ]

1055
01:48:57,054 --> 01:48:59,648
0h!

1056
01:49:01,214 --> 01:49:05,366
Now you know how to fly an airplane?
