1057
01:49:05,454 --> 01:49:08,332
0w! Now you stop it!
You behave yourself now!

1058
01:49:38,094 --> 01:49:40,244
[ Explosions ]

1059
01:50:01,134 --> 01:50:04,046
- 0h!
- [ Mariner Grunting ]

1060
01:50:16,054 --> 01:50:18,170
[ Explosion ]

1061
01:50:30,494 --> 01:50:32,371
[ Explosion ]

1062
01:50:37,014 --> 01:50:38,845
[ Helen ]
lt's going down.

1063
01:50:38,934 --> 01:50:43,928
