right down on top of it.

1064
01:50:43,974 --> 01:50:46,044
- Hurry, Gregor!
- [ Gregor ] Don't worry.

1065
01:50:46,134 --> 01:50:47,965
Hurry.

1066
01:50:51,774 --> 01:50:54,686
[ Clanging, Rumbling ]

1067
01:50:59,254 --> 01:51:02,291
Enola! Up here!

1068
01:51:02,334 --> 01:51:04,245
Grab on!

1069
01:51:09,134 --> 01:51:11,011
[ Gregor ]
Are they on yet?

1070
01:51:14,254 --> 01:51:16,927
- [ Gregor ] What is it?
- [ Helen ] l don't know!

1071
01:51:17,014 --> 01:51:18,732
No!

1072
01:51:27,614 --> 01:51:32,813
Gotcha! l'm gonna rip
