1073
01:51:36,334 --> 01:51:38,211
[ Yelling ]

1074
01:51:41,534 --> 01:51:44,048
[ Enraged Shout ]

1075
01:51:46,494 --> 01:51:48,928
Pull! Almost.

1076
01:51:52,614 --> 01:51:55,128
[ Helen, Gregor Laughing ]

1077
01:51:56,454 --> 01:51:59,969
[ Explosion ]

1078
01:52:26,414 --> 01:52:28,086
- [ Shrieks ]
- [ Helen ] No!

1079
01:52:28,134 --> 01:52:30,967
- [ Enola Screaming ]
- [ Helen ] No! Enola!

1080
01:52:32,254 --> 01:52:34,609
